	condition on USE_REGEX.
	* libbalsa/filter-private.h: ditto.
	* libbalsa/mime.c: (mark_urls, libbalsa_insert_with_url,
	libbalsa_unwrap_selection): ditto.
	* libbalsa/misc.h: ditto.
	* src/balsa-app.c: ditto.
	* src/balsa-app.h: ditto.
